<div class="jumbotron">
    <h1>Welcome in MoWin</h1>
    <p class="lead">This is server part of MoWin system which allows browse users, logs, statistics and more.</p>
</div>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Users</h2>
        <p>Users part of application allows epxlore available users, create new users, changing their roles and passwords.</p>
        <p>@Html.ActionLink("Check Users", "Index", "Users", new { area = "" }, new { @class = "btn btn-info" })</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Logs</h2>
        <p>Logs allows you to check which calls has been made according to date. It has powerfull filters so you can filter information by any property you want.</p>
        <p>@Html.ActionLink("Check Logs", "Index", "Log", new { area = "" }, new { @class = "btn btn-info" })</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Statistics</h2>
        <p>Statistics allow you to watch which scripts are most used, which users are most active and so one.</p>
        <p>@Html.ActionLink("Check Statistics", "Stats", "Log", new { area = "" }, new { @class = "btn btn-info" })</p>
    </div>
</div>
